e combination of articles in this volume illustrates the potential of number marking and offers insights that contribute our understanding of how grammatical number is applied and categorised in languages.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Apr 2024) 0aGrammar, Comparative and generalxNumber. 0aTypology (Linguistics). 4aSingulativ. 4aSprachkontakt. 4aZahlwort. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / General.2bisacsh  aTonal Marking, Singulative, Borrowing, Competing Strategies.1 aArbes, Deborah, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aArbes, Deborah, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aArkhipov, Alexandre, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCompes, Isabel, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aElnur, Elsadig Omda Ibrahim, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGayler, Katharina, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNurmio, Silva, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aStolz, Thomas, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2023 Part 1z978311117578208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023 Englishz978311131929208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023z9783111318912oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Linguistics 2023 Englishz978311131916208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Linguistics 2023z9783111318240oZDB-23-DSP0 cEPUBz97831109866240 cprintz978311099787340uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311098660040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/978311098660042